BobUI 5.1.1 is a bug-fix release. It maintains both forward and backward
compatibility (source and binary) with BobUI 5.1.0.

For more details, refer to the online documentation included in this
distribution. The documentation is also available online:

  http://bobui-project.org/doc/bobui-5.1/

The BobUI version 5.1 series is binary compatible with the 5.0.x series.
Applications compiled for 5.0 will continue to run with 5.1.

Some of the changes listed in this file include issue tracking numbers
corresponding to tasks in the BobUI Bug Tracker:

  http://bugreports.bobui-project.org/

Each of these identifiers can be entered in the bug tracker to obtain more
information about a particular change.


****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

 - Add support for Visual Studio 2013
 - Remove obsolete 'register' C keyword
 - Speed up font database loading with fontconfig
 - [BOBUIBUG-32284] Fix incomplete override of QIODevice::open in QProcess and QLocalSocket

